Privacy Policy for Kiganjani Afya Check

1. Introduction

Welcome to Kiganjani Afya Check ("we", "our", or "us"). Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application. Please read this policy carefully. If you do not agree with the terms of this policy, please do not access the application.

2. Information We Collect

We may collect information about you in a variety of ways, including:

Personal Data: Personally identifiable information, such as your name, email address, and health data (such as weight, height,age, etc.) that you voluntarily give to us when you register with the application or when you choose to participate in various activities related to the application.

Health Data: Information about your health status, medical conditions, and other related metrics that you input into the app.

Usage Data: Information about your interactions with the application, including the time and date of your visits, your IP address, and your device information.

3. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect in various ways, including to:

Provide, operate, and maintain our application.
Improve, personalize, and expand our application.
Understand and analyze how you use our application.
